lt=\"Vestibulinho 1 Semetre 2024\" class=\"wp-image-148\" width=\"680\" height=\"394\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></section>\n<!-- /wp:group -->','Vestibulinho','','inherit','closed','closed','','103-revision-v1','','','2023-11-16 22:32:54','2023-11-17 01:32:54','',103,'http://localhost:8000/?p=151',0,'revision','',0),(152,1,'2023-11-16 22:35:22','2023-11-17 01:35:22','<!-- wp:acf/banner-primary {\"name\":\"acf/banner-primary\",\"data\":{\"category\":\"Vestibulinho\",\"_category\":\"field_banner_primary_category\",\"wysiwyg_content\":\"\\u003ch2\\u003eDIVULGAÇÃO DO RESULTADO RECURSO/CORREÇÃO/ANÁLISE DE DOCUMENTOS\\u003c/h2\\u003e\",\"_wysiwyg_content\":\"field_banner_primary_wysiwyg_content\",\"button\":{\"title\":\"Acessar\",\"url\":\"#Acessar\",\"target\":\"\"},\"_button\":\"field_banner_primary_button\",\"image\":98,\"_image\":\"field_banner_primary_image\",\"image_right\":\"0\",\"_image_right\":\"field_banner_primary_image_right\"},\"align\":\"\",\"mode\":\"edit\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"tagName\":\"section\",\"className\":\"container\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<section class=\"wp-block-group container\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":148,\"width\":680,\"height\":394,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/tarja_site-1024x594.png\" alt=\"Vestibulinho 1 Semetre 2024\" class=\"wp-image-148\" width=\"680\" height=\"394\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Marcado para 10 de dezembro, o <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.vestibulinhoetec.com.br/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Vestibulinho das Escolas Técnicas Estaduais (Etecs)</a> é a porta de entrada para os cursos do Ensino Técnico, Médio integrado ao Técnico, Ensino Médio em dif